  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t洛陽是中華民國（大陸淪陷區）的一座歷史名城，古稱「中京」、「洛邑」、「神都」、「帝京」、「成周」、「中國」等。在歷史上，洛陽曾經是東周、東漢、曹魏、西晉、隋（煬帝遷都洛陽）、唐（武周時期）、後唐等朝代的首都，並且作為華北平原上的一個歷史、宗教、與文化中心，見證了中原文明數千年來的興衰與演化。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n這樣一座歷史名城不應該被遺忘。願有朝一日我們也能光復洛陽，時代革命。窩小人家蒐集了網路上各路遊客和攝影師拍攝的一些圖片，給諸位品蔥志士欣賞：<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9aZzByZ3plLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zg0rgze.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zg0rgze.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zg0rgze.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽紫微宮城的正南門——應天門。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9HT3N3Wm5mLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/GOswZnf.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/GOswZnf.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GOswZnf.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽民主街。圖片來源：洛陽天天旅行社）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS95TG9ONHNzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/yLoN4ss.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yLoN4ss.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yLoN4ss.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽在地圖上的位置。圖片來源：郭如意/星球研究所）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9uaHA1MFdVLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/nhp50WU.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nhp50WU.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nhp50WU.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽麗景門。圖片來源：欣傳媒）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9mMm9wZnNtLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/f2opfsm.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/f2opfsm.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f2opfsm.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽麗景門。圖片來源：dreamtime）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9FNHZ6WU5RLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/E4vzYNQ.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/E4vzYNQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E4vzYNQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽的復古風商業老街——明清街。圖片來源：痞客邦 | Quby）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9CdlRBZGg0LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/BvTAdh4.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BvTAdh4.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BvTAdh4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（紫微宮城西側的九州池夜景。九州池是武則天的后宮花園，湖中有多個小島。在改革開放時期，這裡是浮法玻璃集團的所在地。西元2009年，匪偽洛陽當局據稱撥款十億軟妹幣，將浮法玻璃遷走，用了歷時十年的時間，重建了唐朝風格的九州池，並於西元2019年4月27日開園。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9zcFdNeWZPLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/spWMyfO.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/spWMyfO.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/spWMyfO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（九州池岸上的瑤光殿仿古建築。圖片來源：Trip香港）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9Rc2R5MTVjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qsdy15c.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qsdy15c.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qsdy15c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（九州池園林與瑤光殿。圖片來源：百度）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9kM1MwYlhILmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/d3S0bXH.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/d3S0bXH.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d3S0bXH.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（九州池園林空拍。圖片來源：百度）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9zNldTTGFyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/s6WSLar.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/s6WSLar.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s6WSLar.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽南郊伊水河畔的龍門石窟。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9EMENnazBOLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/D0Cgk0N.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/D0Cgk0N.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D0Cgk0N.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（鳥瞰紫微宮城。匪偽洛陽當局在改革開放後，修復了洛陽的部分古蹟，以吸引遊客參觀。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9MNmZSd1JuLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/L6fRwRn.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/L6fRwRn.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/L6fRwRn.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（紫微宮城與應天門。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9lVnJVZ2VjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/eVrUgec.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eVrUgec.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eVrUgec.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（明堂是唐朝武周時期宴請百官的場所，曾經是一座高達98(?)米的巨型木製建築。現在這個小建築模仿了部分武周時期的內裝。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9tWWg3UUc4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/mYh7QG8.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mYh7QG8.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mYh7QG8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（紫微宮城的天堂，即過去則天武后禮佛的地方，相當於唐帝國的國家佛堂。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9YeUY1QlhLLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/XyF5BXK.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XyF5BXK.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XyF5BXK.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（漢、魏時代紫微故宮的復原圖。圖片來源：神都網。）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8zMU9hTU5JLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/31OaMNI.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/31OaMNI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/31OaMNI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（武周時期的名堂復原圖。圖片來源：紀錄片《大唐帝陵》/百度百科）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9teDJzYk1SLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/mx2sbMR.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mx2sbMR.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mx2sbMR.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（明堂內部。圖片來源：跟隨歷史去旅行）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9NendTNGdxLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/MzwS4gq.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/MzwS4gq.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MzwS4gq.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（明堂內部的武則天與百官壁畫。武則天晚年寫了長達一百篇的回憶錄，名為《垂拱集》。圖片來源：跟隨歷史去旅行）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9nZ1NDRlZ3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/ggSCFVw.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ggSCFVw.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ggSCFVw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽伊水也稱伊河的晝間景觀。圖片來源：Trip香港）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9OamFYdGpCLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjaXtjB.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjaXtjB.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjaXtjB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽城郊的孟津黃河濕地。圖片來源：ChinaDiscovery網）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9xUWRuQWM2LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/qQdnAc6.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qQdnAc6.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qQdnAc6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽老君山道院。圖片來源：ChinaDiscovery網）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9xRTRSZ3NRLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/qE4RgsQ.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qE4RgsQ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qE4RgsQ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\r\n（洛陽郊區新安縣的龍潭大峽谷。圖片來源：醉美中國遊）\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
